## Setup private settings, keys etc.

```bash
./setups/secrets.sh email@domain.com
./setups/official/git.sh
```

## Development

Install pre commit hooks

```bash
pipx install pre-commit
pre-commit install
```

Install kitty terminfo when using users over SSH

```bash
cd ~
curl -O https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kovidgoyal/kitty/master/terminfo/kitty.terminfo
tic -x kitty.terminfo
```
